---
import MarketingLayout from '../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout title="Terms and Conditions" description="MakerVault terms and conditions. One-time purchase license with 1 year of updates.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-2xl pt-24 pb-16">
    <h1 class="mb-8 text-center font-bold text-4xl">Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 7, 2026</p>

      <h2>License</h2>
      <p>MakerVault is licensed software, not sold. When you purchase MakerVault, you receive a perpetual, non-exclusive license to use the application on up to 2 computers that you own or control.</p>

      <h2>Free trial</h2>
      <p>MakerVault offers a 7-day free trial with full functionality. No credit card is required. After the trial period, a license key is required to continue using the application.</p>

      <h2>Pricing and updates</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>MakerVault is a one-time purchase of $59 USD.</li>
        <li>Your purchase includes 1 year of software updates from the date of purchase.</li>
        <li>After the update period expires, you keep the last version you received and can continue using it forever.</li>
        <li>You may renew your update access at any time to receive new versions.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Refunds</h2>
      <p>If you're not satisfied with MakerVault, contact us within 14 days of purchase at <a href="mailto:hello@makervaultapp.com">hello@makervaultapp.com</a> for a full refund.</p>

      <h2>Your data</h2>
      <p>MakerVault is a local-first application. All your data (file index, tags, notes, metadata) is stored on your computer. We do not have access to your data. You are responsible for backing up your data. See our <a href="/legal/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>MakerVault is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We are not liable for any damages arising from the use of the software. MakerVault indexes and organizes your files but does not modify your original files on disk.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@makervaultapp.com">hello@makervaultapp.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</MarketingLayout>
